<li id="cite_note-10"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news"><a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/2956925.stm" class="external text" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/2956925.stm" rel="nofollow">"'Earliest writing' found in China."</a>. <a href="/wiki/BBC" title="BBC">BBC</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/2956925.stm" class="external free" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/2956925.stm" rel="nofollow">http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/2956925.stm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-03-30</span>.  "Signs carved into 8,600-year-old tortoise shells found in China may be the earliest written words, say archaeologists."</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=%27Earliest+writing%27+found+in+China.&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BBBC%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.bbc.co.uk%2F2%2Fhi%2Fscience%2Fnature%2F2956925.stm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Writing"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
